<sect1 id="dir_734da5e9060906fd2f909892a288292e_1autotoc_md288">
<title>helios::engine::runtime::world</title><para>World state management and per-frame update context.</para>
</sect1>
<sect1 id="dir_734da5e9060906fd2f909892a288292e_1autotoc_md289">
<title>Overview</title><para>This module provides the core classes for managing game state during runtime. The <computeroutput>GameWorld</computeroutput> class serves as the central registry for all GameObjects, while <computeroutput>UpdateContext</computeroutput> provides the frame context passed to systems during updates.</para>
</sect1>
